{
  "stem": "22869.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And meanwhile, we get the good news that the-- our Nazi commandant who was there with the two horses-- he got shot in both feet, in both legs.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they had to take him away with an ambulance to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we're, like, there was a-- a-- a sigh of relief because we thought, oh, death penalty, it was just removed from all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And a couple of his horses also got shot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were not dead, but they got shot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So in all the mish-mash that was going around there-- you can imagine, after a shooting and things, and the damages, and the trains were shot, and the-- with the civilian people bringing food-- someone of the SS men didn't want the horses to suffer.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He shot them dead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they gave us permission that everybody who wants to can take a piece of meat from the-- from the horses.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So it took them I don't know how many hours, you know, to distribute the food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we at least ate for a while well, which wasn't so healthy either because once you stuff your stomach after you didn't eat for so long, you usually become sick.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they told us that within a certain time the locomotive will be repaired.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We'll get a second locomotive, and we'll be moving on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so after they gave us permission that everybody can take along some-- from the horses the meat, so we all ran there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have any knives.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember how we cut a piece of meat, but somehow we got a hold of a piece of horse meat.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a friend of mine found at the station a big sack of probably 50 or 100 kilo dried onions.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
